<SYNC Start=2044949><P Class=KRCC>
순정아...
<SYNC Start=2048649><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2049930><P Class=KRCC>
얼... 얼마나 다친 거야?
<SYNC Start=2052160><P Class=KRCC>
